message: Hi Bob, I'm interested in selling my product.  I think it would be incredibly valuable for you, and I'm aiming for a price around $11,000. What do you think?
Hello Alice, thank you for considering my budget. I appreciate the value of your product, but I am only willing to pay up to $9,000. Let me know if this is something we can work with.
Hi Bob, thanks for your offer. I understand your position, but $9,000 is a bit too low for me. Could we meet in the middle at $10,000? I'm confident you'll see a great return on this investment.
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I am still not able to go above $9,500 for the product. This is the highest I can offer while staying within my budget.
